{
  "info": {
    "name": "Almacenes INIAF - API",
    "description": "Coleccion de la API del Sistema de Almacenes.\n\nBASE: http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n\nUSO RAPIDO:\n1. Corre el backend (pnpm start:dev) y el seed (pnpm prisma db seed).\n2. Ejecuta 'Auth > Login' con el usuario admin/admin123. El accessToken y refreshToken se guardan solos en las variables de la coleccion (script en la pestana Tests del request).\n3. El resto de requests ya mandan 'Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}' heredado a nivel de coleccion.\n\nVariables editables en la pestana 'Variables' de la coleccion.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1" },
    { "key": "fileBaseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "usuario", "value": "admin" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "admin123" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "itemId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "imagenUrl", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"usuario\": \"{{usuario}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "  console.log('Tokens guardados. Rol:', res.user && res.user.rol);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('login 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "refresh"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (perfil)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "me"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Usuarios",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "rol", "value": "solicitador", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "unidadId", "value": "1", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "almacenId", "value": "1", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear (solicitador: unidad + almacén)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Nuevo Solicitador\",\n  \"usuario\": \"solic_test\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"rol\": \"solicitador\",\n  \"unidadId\": 1,\n  \"almacenId\": 1\n}"
            },
            "description": "Campos requeridos por rol (validado en el service): solicitador -> unidad + almacen; aprobador -> unidad + almacen (unico por unidad); responsable_almacen y central -> almacen (unico por almacen); observador_almacen -> almacenesObservados; admin/super_admin -> ninguno. Mandar un campo que el rol no lleva devuelve 400."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear (aprobador: unidad + almacén)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Nuevo Aprobador\",\n  \"usuario\": \"aprob_test\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"rol\": \"aprobador\",\n  \"unidadId\": 1,\n  \"almacenId\": 1\n}"
            },
            "description": "El aprobador ahora requiere unidad Y almacen (igual que solicitador). Sin almacenId responde 400 'El rol aprobador requiere un almacen'. Sigue siendo unico por unidad: un segundo aprobador activo en la misma unidad responde 409."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Nombre Editado\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (baja logica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios", "1"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Unidades",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["unidades"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Unidad de Prueba\",\n  \"sigla\": \"UP-TEST\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Unidad Editada\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades", "1"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Almacenes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["almacenes"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Almacen de Prueba\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Almacen Editado\",\n  \"activo\": true\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (baja logica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes", "1"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Partidas",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar plano (paginado + filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["partidas"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "39700", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "seleccionable", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "nivel", "value": "1", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "padreId", "value": "1", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Arbol jerarquico",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/arbol",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["partidas", "arbol"],
              "query": [{ "key": "soloActivas", "value": "true", "disabled": true }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["partidas", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Activar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/1/activar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["partidas", "1", "activar"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/1/desactivar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["partidas", "1", "desactivar"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Items",
      "description": "Catalogo compartido por todos los almacenes. Escritura solo super_admin/admin; lectura para cualquier autenticado.\n\nIMAGEN (1 por item, filesystem): usar 'Subir/Reemplazar imagen' con body form-data, campo 'imagen' de tipo File. Se procesa a WebP y se guarda en /uploads/items. La respuesta trae 'imagenUrl' (ej. /uploads/items/3-8eeae5d8.webp), servible como estatica publica (sin token) en {{fileBaseUrl}}{{imagenUrl}}.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado + filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["items"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "39700", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "partidaId", "value": "4", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["items", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear (solo super_admin/admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"descripcion\": \"Item de prueba\",\n  \"unidadMedida\": \"UNIDAD\",\n  \"partidaId\": 4\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('itemId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('itemId guardado:', res.id, res.codigo);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar (solo super_admin/admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["items", "{{itemId}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"descripcion\": \"Descripcion editada\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Subir/Reemplazar imagen (form-data)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}/imagen", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["items", "{{itemId}}", "imagen"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "imagen", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Archivo JPEG/PNG/WebP, max 5 MB. Se convierte a WebP <=1024px." }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Elige un archivo en la pestana Body > form-data, campo 'imagen' (tipo File). NO poner Content-Type manual: Postman arma el multipart boundary solo. La respuesta trae 'imagenUrl'."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.imagenUrl) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('imagenUrl', res.imagenUrl);",
                  "  console.log('imagenUrl:', res.imagenUrl, '-> abrir en', pm.collectionVariables.get('fileBaseUrl') + res.imagenUrl);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('subida 200/201', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Ver imagen (estatica publica, sin token)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{fileBaseUrl}}{{imagenUrl}}", "host": ["{{fileBaseUrl}}{{imagenUrl}}"] },
            "description": "Sirve el archivo directo desde /uploads (fuera del JWT). Usa la variable imagenUrl que dejo la subida. En un navegador o <img src> se ve igual."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Quitar imagen",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}/imagen", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["items", "{{itemId}}", "imagen"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (baja logica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["items", "{{itemId}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Proveedores",
      "description": "Escritura solo super_admin/admin. Lectura tambien para responsable_almacen (selector de proveedor al registrar un Ingreso).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado + filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["proveedores"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "distribuidora", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "q busca en nombre, nit y contacto."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["proveedores", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear (solo super_admin/admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["proveedores"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Distribuidora La Paz S.R.L.\",\n  \"nit\": \"1023456789\",\n  \"telefono\": \"22334455\",\n  \"contacto\": \"Juan Perez\",\n  \"direccion\": \"Av. Arce 1234, La Paz\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Solo nombre es requerido (NO es unico: la razon social se escribe de formas distintas). nit es opcional pero unico si se envia; pueden convivir varios proveedores sin NIT."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear sin NIT (minimo)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["proveedores"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Ferreteria del Sur\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar (solo super_admin/admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["proveedores", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Distribuidora La Paz S.R.L. (editado)\",\n  \"telefono\": \"22334466\",\n  \"contacto\": \"Maria Quispe\",\n  \"activo\": true\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Limpiar NIT (cadena vacia -> null)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["proveedores", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nit\": \"\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Enviar el NIT como cadena vacia lo normaliza a null (libera el indice unico)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (baja logica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/proveedores/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["proveedores", "1"] },
            "description": "Nunca se borra fisicamente: sera referenciado por Ingreso y romperia el Kardex."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
